[06:19] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'inspects your video one piece at a time, and then it breaks it down into a 360° sphere with six main components. Each generates a face of the 3D scene at a time in short chunks. And then it uses'

[06:33] [scene:talk]
